      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. GIVE ME BUCKS boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and four minors from eight tries. Below best last time at this track (22.25) in a Free For All, finishing a 6 length fifth. Looks a leading chance on best. 8. DIVA ERADICATOR was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her slick win three back, getting around this track over 390m in 21.78. Has the ability and looks a key chance. 3. CAKE IS GREAT is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 21.82 beating Diva Eradicator. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from five attempts. Will go close again if runs up to latest. 4. SUPER LEON hit the frame latest (26.00) when third at this track in a Mix 5. Has four wins already from this draw.\",\"runners\":[1,8,3,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
